@EmailSim_HostAddress = http://localhost:5227

### Get stats (emailCount, agentCount, totalCount, maxLimit)
GET {{EmailSim_HostAddress}}/api/stats

### Get pending emails (dequeues and returns new emails)
GET {{EmailSim_HostAddress}}/api/emails/pending

### Reset counts (歸零後 Game Loop 恢復)
POST {{EmailSim_HostAddress}}/api/reset

### Click check - FakeLink 虛假連結
POST {{EmailSim_HostAddress}}/api/email/click
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender": "info@paypal-support.org",
  "subject": "收到一筆新的付款",
  "content": "您收到一筆 $500 USD 的付款...",
  "isPhishing": true,
  "type": 1,
  "warningMessage": ""
}

### Click check - UrgentThreat 威脅語氣
POST {{EmailSim_HostAddress}}/api/email/click
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender": "no-reply@hsbc-secure-mail.com",
  "subject": "您的帳戶已被暫時鎖定",
  "content": "偵測到異常活動...",
  "isPhishing": true,
  "type": 2,
  "warningMessage": ""
}

### Click check - GiftScam 中獎詐騙
POST {{EmailSim_HostAddress}}/api/email/click
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender": "rewards@apple-store.com",
  "subject": "恭喜！您獲得了一台 iPhone 16 Pro",
  "content": "您被選為本月幸運用戶...",
  "isPhishing": true,
  "type": 3,
  "warningMessage": ""
}

### Click check - safe email
POST {{EmailSim_HostAddress}}/api/email/click
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender": "library@cityu.edu.hk",
  "subject": "圖書逾期通知",
  "content": "您借閱的《Data Structures》已逾期...",
  "isPhishing": false,
  "type": 0
}

